### Both trackers with their runs
GET http://localhost:4105/pipeline/Pipelines?$filter=startswith(name,'Shipments_')&$expand=runs($orderby=startTime desc;$top=3)

### Full refresh for DEV only — deletes DEV rows only, replays from source.
POST http://localhost:4105/pipeline/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"Shipments_DEV","mode":"full","trigger":"manual"}

### Confirm PROD rows untouched.
GET http://localhost:4105/odata/v4/example/Shipments?$filter=source eq 'PROD'
